value.0: This small, dizzy humanoid would be merely a pest, if not for its sheer force of inebriation. It has a flat face with a broad nose, and pointed ears, and a wide mouth with a stupid-looking grin and small, sharp fangs. Its pupils are dilated beyond the borders of its beady eyes, and it seems to be oblivious to its surroundings. Jaundiced skin and shabby clothes are both streaked with bright splashes of color. This one forgoes its armor in favor of a silly hat and loincloth.
